snippet.title: Funkin' Corruption: REIMAGINED | EVIL Boyfriend vs Daddy Dearest FINAL BATTLE!
snippet.description:
There was meant to be a mechanic, but it was removed for video purposes.

Funkin' Corruption: Reimagined is based off of Phantom Fear's corruption, but with an entirely twisted storyline and new songs!
